ment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franveer-allahbadia-controversy-video-of-raghu-ram-and-rajiv-lakshman-talking-about-samay-raina-and-his-show-indias-got-latent-goes-viral%2Farticleshow%2F118214809.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Wives%2C%20Partners%20With%20India%20For%20CT%202025.%20Senior%20Enquired%2C%20He%20Was%20Told...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFamilies%20will%20not%20be%20accompanying%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20players%20heading%20to%20Dubai%20on%20February%2015%20for%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20as%20the%20BCCI's%20new%20travel%20policy%20comes%20into%20effect%20for%20the%20first%20time%20with%20this%20tournament.%20The%20Indian%20team%20starts%20its%20campaign%20in%20Dubai%20against%20Bangladesh%20on%20February%2020%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20marquee%20clash%20against%20arch-rivals%20Pakistan%20(February%2023)%20and%20the%20final%20preliminary%20face-off%20with%20New%20Zealand%20on%20March%202.%20The%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20squad%20will%20play%20its%20games%20in%20Dubai%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20tournament%20unfolds%20from%20February%2019%20in%20Pakistan%20across%20three%20venues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20the%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20tour%20is%20just%20over%20three%20weeks%20even%20if%20the%20final%20on%20March%209%20is%20taken%20into%20consideration%2C%20the%20BCCI%20will%20not%20allow%20families%20to%20accompany%20the%20players.%20As%20per%20the%20new%20policy%2C%20families%20can%20be%20with%20players%20for%20a%20maximum%20of%20two%20weeks%20during%20a%20tour%20which%20is%20of%2045%20days%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20anything%20changes%20then%20it%20is%20different%20but%20as%20of%20now%2C%20the%20players%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20accompanied%20by%20their%20wives%20or%20partners%20for%20this%20tour.%20One%20of%20the%20senior%20players%20had%20enquired%20about%20it%20and%20he%20was%20told%20that%20the%20policy%20decision%20will%20be%20followed%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20BCCI%20source%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20tour%20is%20of%20less%20than%20one%20month%2C%20families%20won't%20be%20accompanying%20the%20players.%20But%20if%20exceptions%20are%20made%2C%20I%20think%20that%20individual%20will%20have%20to%20bear%20the%20full%20expenses%20as%20BCCI%20won't%20be%20covering%20any%20cost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20policy%20document%20states%3A%20%26quot%3BPlayers%20absent%20from%20India%20for%20more%20than%2045%20days%20during%20overseas%20tours%20can%20be%20joined%20by%20their%20partners%20and%20children%20(under%2018)%20for%20one%20visit%20per%20series%20(format%20wise)%20of%20up%20to%20a%20two-week%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20deviation%20from%20this%20policy%20must%20be%20pre-approved%20by%20the%20coach%2C%20captain%20and%20GM%20Operations.%20Additional%20expenses%20outside%20the%20visitors'%20period%20will%20not%20be%20covered%20by%20the%20BCCI.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20families%20will%20be%20there%20with%20the%20team%20during%20the%20five-Test%20tour%20of%20England%20in%20June-July-August%20as%20the%20five-Test.%20The%20window%20for%20their%20two-week%20stay%20during%20the%20trip%20will%20be%20worked%20out%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rules%20were%20drafted%20after%20India's%20horror%20tour%20of%20Australia%20during%20which%20the%20team%20was%20outplayed%201-3%2C%20leading%20to%20speculation%20about%20lack%20of%20discipline%20and%20cohesion%20in%20the%20dressing%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739447040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F3vsoa1d_virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-afp_625x300_05_February_2