E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Green%20Energy%20had%20been%20under%20protracted%20discussions%20with%20the%20Ceylon%20Electricity%20Board%20(CEB)%20and%20government%20departments%20for%20over%20two%20years%20to%20set%20up%20two%20484%20megawatt%20(MW)%20renewable%20energy%20wind%20farms%20in%20Sri%20Lanka's%20Mannar%20and%20Pooneryn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20included%20the%20associated%20transmission%20system%2C%20as%20also%20additional%20220%20kilovolt%20(kV)%20and%20400%20kV%20transmission%20network%20expansion%20to%20carry%20power%20to%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20island%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Green%20Energy%20said%20till%20date%20it%20has%20spent%20some%20%245%20million%20on%20predevelopment%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20its%20executives%20have%20been%20holding%20talks%20with%20CEB%20and%20Sri%20Lankan%20ministry%20officials%20in%20Colombo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20It%20was%20learnt%20that%20another%20Cabinet%20appointed%20negotiations%20committee%20(CANC)%20and%20Project%20Committee%20(PC)%20would%20be%20constituted%20to%20renegotiate%20the%20project%20proposal.%20This%20aspect%20was%20deliberated%20at%20the%20Board%20of%20our%20company%20and%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20while%20the%20company%20fully%20respects%20the%20sovereign%20rights%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20its%20choices%2C%20it%20would%20respectfully%20withdraw%20from%20the%20said%20project%2C%26quot%3B%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20bow%20out%2C%20we%20wish%20to%20reaffirm%20that%20we%20would%20always%20be%20available%20for%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20government%20to%20have%20us%20undertake%20any%20development%20opportunity%2C%20if%20it%20ever%20considers%20Adani%20Group%20to%20participate.%20We%20wish%20to%20convey%20our%20best%20wishes%20and%20gratitude%20to%20the%20government%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%20for%20the%20opportunity%20of%20engagement%2C%26quot%3B%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20company%20withdrew%20from%20building%20the%20two%20projects%2C%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20teams%20had%20several%20rounds%20of%20discussions%20with%20state-appointed%20committees%20and%20after%20more%20than%2014%20rounds%20of%20discussions%2C%20approval%20was%20given%20on%20tariff%2C%20fixed%20for%2020%20years%2C%20for%20the%20power%20purchase%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdani%20Green%20also%20worked%20on%20all%20clearances%20and%20licences.%20With%20the%20exception%20of%20Mannar%20environmental%20approval%20and%20an%20associated%20Supreme%20Court%20case%2C%20we%20have%20procured%20almost%20all%20clearances.%20Similarly%2C%20we%20have%20worked%20on%20lands%20for%20the%20project%2C%20as%20well%20as%20associated%20transmission%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Green%20Energy%20won%20the%20approval%20in%20February%202023%20to%20invest%20%24442%20million%20and%20develop%20the%20484%20MW%20wind%20power%20plants%20in%20Mannar%20town%20and%20Pooneryn%20village%2C%20both%20located%20in%20the%20northern%20province%20of%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Green%20Energy%20Ltd%20(AGEL)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20renewable%20companies%20in%20India%2C%20with%20a%20current%20project%20portfolio%20of%2020%2C434%20MW.%20AGEL%20develops%2C%20builds%2C%20owns%2C%20operates%20and%20maintains%20utility-scale%20grid-connected%20solar%20and%20wind%20farm%20projects.%20The%20electricity%20generated%20is%20supplied%20to%20central%20and%20state%20government%20entities%20and%20government-backed%20corporations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739445480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fn9uj38go_adani-green-energy_625x300_14_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%2