d%20learning%20about%20sex-selective%20abortion%20in%20India%2C%20a%20now-illegal%20practice%20where%20families%20terminate%20the%20pregnancies%20if%20the%20fetuses%20are%20female.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20Bhatnagar%20had%20only%20been%20coding%20for%20a%20few%20years%2C%20but%20she%20said%20that%20her%20motivation%20to%20help%20solve%20the%20problem%20outweighed%20her%20technical%20ability.%20She%20found%20a%20cofounder%2C%20Gaurav%20Bhattacharya%2C%20and%20the%20pair%20developed%20AI%20software%20that%20identified%20risk%20factors%20that%20could%20determine%20if%20someone%20might%20be%20planning%20to%20abort%20their%20baby%20based%20on%20gender.%20The%20Indian%20government%20eventually%20distributed%20their%20tech%20to%20ultrasound%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20experience%2C%20Bhatnagar%20said%20that%20she%20was%20passionate%20enough%20about%20solving%20the%20problem%20and%20willing%20to%20think%20creatively%20about%20potential%20solutions%20to%20overcome%20her%20lack%20of%20advanced%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMotivation%20supersedes%20ability%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20always%20learn%20how%20to%20code%2C%20but%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20motivation%2C%20it%20won't%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20so%20passionate%20about%20the%20cause%2C%20I%20was%20willing%20to%20fail%20a%20thousand%20times.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202cf8ddf-fe75-40b6-8996-e443dfb5a590%5C%22%3EThe%20competitive%20edge%20of%20creativity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBhatnagar%20and%20Bhattacharya%20have%20continued%20to%20work%20together%20and%20are%20currently%20the%20co-founders%20of%20Jeeva%2C%20an%20AI%20agent%20startup%20focused%20on%20automating%20customer%20retention%20and%20revenue%20growth.%20The%20startup%2C%20previously%20known%20as%20Involve%20AI%2C%20has%20raised%20more%20than%20%2420%20million%20in%20VC%20funding%2C%20most%20recently%20in%20a%20%2416%20million%20Series%20A%20round%20in%202021%20led