g%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-peace-push-not-a-betrayal-of-ukraine-hegseth%2Famp_articleshow%2F118209656.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-peace-push-not-a-betrayal-of-ukraine-hegseth%2Famp_articleshow%2F118209656.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20RSS%20And%20AAP%2C%20A%20Short%20Love%20Story%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20his%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20(AAP)%20defeat%20in%20the%20Delhi%20assembly%20election%20is%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20Indian%20right%20wing%20politics.%20It%20marks%20the%20end%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now%2C%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh's%20(RSS)%20covert%20dalliance%20with%20an%20activist-turned-politician%20who%20grew%20into%20a%20formidable%20adversary%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20the%20last%20time%20that%20the%20RSS%20would%20invest%20in%20a%20non-BJP%20outfit%20on%20the%20national%20stage.%20To%20understand%20it%2C%20we%20have%20to%20go%20to%20the%20roots%20of%20RSS's%20ambitions%20and%20opportunistic%20collaborations%20of%20the%20past%2075%20years%20or%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20from%201980%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20was%20born%20with%20Gandhian%20Socialism%20as%20its%20ideological%20credo%20until%201989%20when%20it%20was%20born%20again%2C%20baptising%20itself%20in%20the%20Hindutva%20wave%20of%20the%20late%20eighties%2C%20the%20party%20remained%20the%20prodigal%20child%20for%20the%20RSS.%20In%20fact%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%20of%20the%20decade%2C%20the%20Sangh%20was%20besotted%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20even%20considering%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20as%20its%20chosen%20one%20for%20a%20brief%20while.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Roots%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20beginning%20of%20Sangh's%20involvement%20in%20mainstream%20electoral%20politics%20is%20generally%20marked%20to%20be%20in%201951%20when%20Syama%20Prasad%20Mookerji%20founded%20the%20Jan%20Sangh%20with%20its%20help.%20Balasaheb%20Deoras%2C%20RSS%20chief%20from%201973%20to%201994%2C%20has%20said%20the%20organisation%20acutely%20felt%20the%20need%20for%20political%20ears%20when%20it%20was%20banned%20following%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20assassination.%20It%20required%20elected%20representatives%20to%20speak%20for%20it%20in%20hostile%20legislatures%20and%20Parliament.%20Deoras%20was%20keen%20that%20RSS%20swayamsevaks%20join%20all%20political%20parties.%20The%20ideal%20proposition%20was%20they%20would%20be%20working%20in%20different%20parties%20during%20the%20day%20and%20attending%20shakhas%20together%20in%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sangh's%20aspiration%20was%20never%20limited%20to%20becoming%20the%20biggest%20organisation%20in%20the%20country%20but%20to%20be%20an%20all-encompassing%2C%20omnipresent%20one%2C%20with%20people%20trained%20in%20its%20nursery%20leading%20every%20aspect%20of%20national%20life.%20Explaining%20founder%20KB%20Hedgewar's%20target%20of%20training%203%25%20of%20the%20urban%20and%202%25%20of%20the%20rural%20populations%20in%20the%20Sangh%20ideology%2C%20Deoras's%20predecessor%2C%20MS%20Golwalkar%2C%20once%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Doctorji%20talked%20about%20one%20percent%20in%20the%20rural%20areas%2C%20he%20meant%20one%20capable%20of%20leading%20the%20remaining%20ninety-nine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Coveted%20Instrument%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20reason%20why%20the%20RSS%20had%20its%20eyes%20set%20on%20the%20Congress%20Party%20and%20the%20genesis%20of%20the%20raging%20rivalry%20between%20the%20two.%20The%20pre-1947%20Congress%20Party%20was%20the%20Big%20Tent%20of%20Indian%20politics.%20After%20Independence%2C%20it%20slowly%20broke%20up%2C%20with%20Communist%20outfits%2C%20socialists%20and%20Hindu%20nationalists%20exiting%20with%20big%20chunks%20of%20it%20over%20the%20next%20few%20decades.%20The%20Jan%20Sangh%2C%20and%20later%20the%20BJP%2C%20not%20only%20appealed%20to%20the%20majority%20Hindus%20but%20also%20were%20inimical%20to%20minorities.%20This%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20the%20RSS%20wanted%20all%20of%20them%20conjoined%20in%20a%20political%20set%20up%20with%20equal%20rights%20and%20powers%2C%20but%20merely%20that%20if%20it%20managed%20to%20take%20control%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20diverse%20outfit%20of%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20could%20achieve%20its%20goals%20quicker.%20Holding%20the%20ideological%20reins%20of%20the%20party%20in%20power%2C%20it%20could%20dictate%20the%20rules%20of%20political%20and%20social%20engagement%20in%20a%20young%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20RSS%20plays%20down%20Golwalkar's%20political%20forays%20because%20of%20its%20constitutional%20commitment%20(written%20to%20abide%20by%20a%20condition%20to%20lift%20its%201948%20ban)%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20politics%2C%20he%20did%20make%20several%20attempts.%20In%201937%2C%20Golwalkar%20himself%20contested%20for%20the%20post%20of%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20when%20it%20held%20organisation%20elections%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%20despite%20GD%20Savarkar's%20backing%2C%20lost%20to%20Indraprakash.%20He%20tried%20to%20get%20entry%20for%20RSS%20volunteers%20into%20the%20Congress%20but%20was%20thwarted%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%20He%20again%20reportedly%20tried%20this%20after%20Nehru's%20death%2C%20appealing%20to%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%2C%20Gulzarilal%20Nanda%2C%20MC%20Chagla%20and%20Swaran%20Singh%20to%20let%20RSS%20men%20into%20key%20organisational%20positions%2C%20but%20to%20no%20avail.%20Golwalkar%20then%20used%20the%20cow%20as%20an%20instrument%20of%20political%20mobilisation%20as%20he%20himself%20confessed%20to%20Verghese%20Kurien%2C%20India's%20milkman.%20It%20did%20not%20deliver%20immediate%20political%20dividends%20but%20ended%20up%20creating%20much%20mayhem%20in%20the%20Capital.%20It%20did%2C%20however%2C%20help%20Jan%20Sangh%20gain%20political%20space%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20post-Emergency%20and%20post-liberalisation%20periods%2C%20the%20RSS%20aligned%20with%20Socialist%20and%20Marxist%20parties.%20It%20stood%20in%20opposition%20to%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20economic%20reforms%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20multinational%20corporations%20and%20computerisation%2C%20issues%20that%20took%20attention%20away%20from%20Hindutva%20and%20Mandal%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStruggle%20With%20Power%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20calibration%20and%20opportunistic%20alliances%20continued%20until%20the%20first%20BJP-led%20government%20was%20in%20power%20with%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20not%20the%20person%20the%20RSS%20really%20wanted%20in%20charge.%20The%20RSS%20and%20the%20BJP%20were%20in%20their%20adversarial%20phase%20after%20the%20government%20fell%20and%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%2C%20led%20by%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20came%20to%20power%20in%202004.%20Some%20enraged%20Sangh%20leaders%20even%20suggested%20severing%20ties%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20floating%20a%20new%20party.%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20then%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20was%20yet%20to%20get%20RSS%20backing%20for%20a%20national%20role.%20The%20gradual%20patch-up%20between%20the%20then%20rising%20Gujarat%20stalwart%20and%20RSS%20began%20only%20in%202008%2C%20but%20the%20latter%20was%20already%20preparing%20the%20groundwork%20to%20unseat%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20government%2C%20which%20was%20going%20after%20its%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneously%2C%20the%20Sangh%20identified%20corruption%20and%20black%20money%20stashed%20abroad%20as%20key%20issues%20to%20corner%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20regime.%20It%20covertly%20backed%20the%20newly%20minted%20Magsaysay%20award%20winner%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20to%20lead%20that%20fight.%20While%20officially%2C%20the%20RSS%20kept%20its%20hands%20off%20Kejriwal's%20anti-corruption%20movement%2C%20its%20volunteers%20mobilised%20support%20for%20agitations%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20In%20private%20conversations%20with%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20even%20held%20up%20Kejriwal%20and%20his%20anti-corruption%20stand%20as%20an%20example%20of%20probity%20in%20public%20life%20worthy%20of%20emulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKejriwal%2C%20The%20'Neutral'%20Politician%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20eventually%20transformed%20his%20agitation%20into%20a%20political%20party%20and%20himself%20into%20a%20politician%2C%20promising%20to%20use%20power%20to%20uplift%20Delhi's%20lot.%20Although%20the%20RSS%20did%20not%20officially%20back%20him%2C%20many%20in%20the%20organisation%20continued%20to%20view%20him%20with%20admiration%2C%20and%20this%20is%20said%20to%20have%20converted%20to%20quiet%20electoral%20support%20too%2C%20which%20partly%20accounted%20for%20the%20vote%20swing%20between%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20elections.%20He%20became%20arguably%20the%20only%20major%20politician%20in%20the%20country%20projecting%20ideological%20neutrality%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwIohhobsWBc%5C%22%3Espouting%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EBharat%20Mata%20ki%20Jai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EVande%20Mataram%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EInquilab%20Zindabad%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20same%20breath.%20He%20unhesitatingly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Felections%2Fgujarat-assembly-election%2Farvind-kejriwal-s-jai-shri-ram-chant-kansa-dig-amid-poster-row-in-gujarat-101665240472100.html%5C%22%3Eembraced%20%3C%2Fa%3EJai%20Shriram%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gettyimages.in%2Fdetail%2Fnews-photo%2Fdelhi-chief-minister-arvind-kejriwal-in-skull-cap-offers-news-photo%2F544928202%5C%22%3Ewore%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20skull%20cap%20at%20Iftar%20parties%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwMhmt0D_rOE%5C%22%3Erecited%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Hanuman%20Chalisa%20on%20national%20television%2C%20and%20alluded%20to%20himself%20as%20an%20avatar%20born%20on%20Lord%20Krishna's%20birthday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kejriwal%20adopted%20Hindutva%20lite%2C%20a%20chasm%20emerged%20between%20the%20RSS%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20peaked%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20when%20party%20president%20JP%20Nadda%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fnadda-on-bjp-rss-ties-we-have-grown-more-capable-now-the-bjp-runs-itself-9336205%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20party%20didn't%20need%20the%20RSS%20anymore.%20Kejriwal%20lost%20no%20time%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Frss-work-reduced-to-laying-carpets-arvind-kejriwal-to-mohan-bhagwat-101727448466062.html%5C%22%3Eindirectly%3C%2Fa%3E%20making%20a%20pitch%20for%20support%20to%20the%20RSS.%20A%20BJP-RSS%20patch-up%20has%20been%2C%20however%2C%20under%20way.%20While%20some%20sections%20of%20the%20RSS%20are%20still%20miffed%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20organisation%20is%20back%20at%20work%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20nodding%20in%20acknowledgement.%20RSS%20volunteers%20worked%20alongside%20BJP%20cadres%20in%20Haryana%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Delhi.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20tweeted%20about%20Mohan%20Bhagwat's%20Vijaydashami%20speech%20last%20year%2C%20something%20he%20had%20not%20done%20for%20almost%20a%20decade.%20Devendra%20Fadnavis-led%20Maharashtra%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fbjp-to-appoint-rss-workers-as-pas-to-its-ministers-101737571872713.html%5C%22%3Einducting%3C%2Fa%3E%20RSS%20volunteers%20as%20ministerial%20staff%20across%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20part%2C%20Kejriwal%20is%20not%20one%20to%20give%20up.%20He%20is%20likely%20to%20focus%20on%20making%20inroads%20in%20new%20political%20territories%2C%20perhaps